snippet.title: Hyper Front by NetEase Games - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
A 5v5 hero-based FPS mobile game, with more tactical opportunities to let your gunplay shine. Enjoy the official trailer of Hyper Front, for a taste of the visually stunning sci-fi universe! Launching in Singapore, Philippines, Malaysia, and Thailand.

Read more - https://gamingonphone.com/news/hyper-front-officially-launched-android-four-countries-of-sea/
